content: Replace the third $10 bill with a $20 bill in a set of bills consisting of a $5 bill, a $10 bill, a $20 bill, and two $50 bills.

In the given set of bills: a $5 bill, a $10 bill, a $20 bill, and two $50 bills, there is only one $10 bill. It seems there is no third $10 bill present in this set to replace. If there's an oversight, please let me know, and I'd be happy to help further!
